"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-golf-2024-1026-1477610-south-koreas-olympians-delight-home-crowd-by-leading\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Tom Kim carded a stunning eagle at the last to join fellow South Korean An Byeong-hun at the top of the Genesis Championship leaderboard.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 0.9635842861487943, \"rank\": 0.02054158102621849, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}, {\"begin\": 65, \"end\": 71, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"score\": 0.996594971286441, \"rank\": 0.003347755660169424, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair, who represented their country at the 2024 Paris Olympics, delighted the home crowd by moving one clear of the chasing pack at 12 under.\", \"from\": 139, \"to\": 284, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kim was forced to grind it out with just one birdie on his front nine, but carded two more at the 10th and 12th.\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 0.9635842861487943, \"rank\": 0.02054158102621849, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He drained a monster 59-foot birdie putt at the 14th which saw him join An and Antoine Rozner, who was in the clubhouse after a 65, at 11 under.\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 479, \"end\": 493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Rozner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Antoine Rozner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Rozner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Rozner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A double bogey followed for Kim at the next, but he responded with a brilliant approach from the rough at the 16th for a birdie.\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 574, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 0.9635842861487943, \"rank\": 0.02054158102621849, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then at the par-five last he landed his second shot to within four feet, which he rolled in for eagle.\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"FULL LEADERBOARD  \\\"It felt great.\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just to finish off the way I finished after that bad break on 15 just makes dinner taste so much better,\\\" Kim said.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 929, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 920, \"end\": 923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 0.9635842861487943, \"rank\": 0.02054158102621849, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously I have made a few mistakes this week but those little things are coming together to back up those mistakes.\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It would be special (to win in my homeland).\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1096, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It would be more special because I have not played back at home since I got to the PGA Tour, so to be able to have a good round tomorrow and finish it off would be really special.\\\"\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1180, \"end\": 1188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PGA_Tour\", \"score\": 0.9999999993606252, \"rank\": 5.997596147828271e-10, \"text\": \"PGA Tour\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PGA_Tour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PGA_Tour\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Overnight leader An had three birdies and two bogeys in his third-round 71.\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I struggled a little bit today,\\\" An said.\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The last two rounds have been almost perfect.\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a little disappointing.\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My shot standard wasn't as sharp as the first two days.\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1532, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was one of those days.\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's golf.\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been great the last few days, it happens and hopefully (it is) better tomorrow.\\\"\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1657, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rozner was joined at 11 under by Francesco Laporta and Ricardo Gouveia, who is in need of strong performance to earn his playing rights for next season.\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1692, \"end\": 1709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francesco_Laporta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Francesco Laporta\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francesco_Laporta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francesco_Laporta\"}, {\"begin\": 1714, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricardo_Gouveia_(golfer)\", \"score\": 0.9999981406284866, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ricardo Gouveia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricardo_Gouveia_(golfer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricardo_Gouveia_(golfer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Source:PA    \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1863, \"end\": 1886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9993664851268295, \"rank\": 0.0006339164685885233, \"text\": \"Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}, {\"begin\": 1888, \"end\": 1895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.999999860182025, \"rank\": 1.3609602791985917e-07, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9 is not responsible for the content of external internet sites.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1929, \"end\": 1932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9835396432123026, \"rank\": 0.013767790549921992, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u